hdtv
====

command line utility to use the HDHomeRun device from the shell

Usage
-----

    hdtv [ OPTIONS ] <COMMAND>

    OPTIONS

        --device <ID>     tuner number (DEFAULT: )

        --tuner <N>     tuner number (DEFAULT: 0)

    COMMANDS

        help            this cruft

        list            list available channels

        view <CC-P>     play channel

Requirements
------------

  * hdhomerun-config
  * vlc

